  <brief_title>A Placebo-controlled Study of Efficacy &amp; Safety of 2 Trough-ranges of Everolimus as Adjunctive Therapy in Patients With Tuberous Sclerosis Complex (TSC) &amp; Refractory Partial-onset Seizures</brief_title>
  <acronym>EXIST-3</acronym>
  <official_title>A Three-arm, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study of the Efficacy and Safety of Two Trough-ranges of Everolimus as Adjunctive Therapy in Patients With Tuberous Sclerosis Complex (TSC) Who Have Refractory Partial-onset Seizures</official_title>
